{"data":[{"date":"14:11 21/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u00e3nh th\u1ed5 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>VOV mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&nbsp;b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/olympic-viet-nam-dung-toan-tay-a-khi-tam-huy-chuong-dang-rat-gan.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>NHM&nbsp;</em><i style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a VOV/VTC</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0ng nh\u1eb1m \u0111em b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ASIAD 2018 v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0110\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n th\u1ec3 thao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c1 m\u00e0 4 n\u0103m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 22/8, kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3, th\u00ednh gi\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd thu\u1ed9c t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c k\u00eanh s\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a VOV v\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c thu\u1ed9c VTC bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c k\u00eanh VTC3, k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh VOVTV, c\u00e1c k\u00eanh ph\u00e1t thanh c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i Ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed VOV.VN, VTCnews v\u00e0 \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng VTCnow.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c do s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o t\u00edch c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VOV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf K\u1ef7 v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c \u0111o\u00e0n th\u1ec3 thao Vi\u1ec7t Nam tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a VOV, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00ed b\u00e1u c\u1ee7a T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n Vingroup v\u00e0 T\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n C\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Vi\u1ec5n th\u00f4ng qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i Viettel.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady NHM c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u1edbi Bahrain s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23 t\u1edbi. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park-168-194864.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park-168-194864.html\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n th\u1ea7y Park</span><br />\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u 19/8 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i. Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5737","checkdouble":"194974"},{"date":"14:46 21/08","title":"HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Vi\u1ec7c xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Malaysia c\u1ee7a BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD.\r\n\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng E sau tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c kh\u00f3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Olympic Iran, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH FIFA th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-olympic-malaysia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Kim Hak-Bum h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u00ec tr\u1eadn thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0m cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea5m HCV t\u1ea1i ASIAD Incheon 2014 c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u00edt d\u1ea7n \u0111i. V\u00e0 HLV Kim Hak-Bum m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Yonhap News, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 lo l\u1eafng. &quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ng\u00e3 r\u1ebd sang con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eadp gh\u1ec1nh \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ecfi \u0111\u00e1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Malaysia l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u1eb7t quan tr\u1ecdng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn khi gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang n\u1eb1m \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t m\u1ed1i nguy hi\u1ec3m \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc&quot;.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-218-cua-doan-ttvn-472-194942.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a HLV Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c&nbsp;l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 Olympic Iran r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. L\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb T\u00e2y \u00c1 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia, Iran v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 30 l\u1ea7n v\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng V\u1ecbnh khi h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 13 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng, 8 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u00e0 9 tr\u1eadn thua. \u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 U23, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n khi trong 7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 4, h\u00f2a m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 thua 2.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Iran tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb v\u1edbi 19/20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U21. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn d\u00e0y d\u1ea1n h\u01a1n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Kim Hak-Bum \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park-168-194864.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/viet-nam-vuot-nhat-ban-dau-an-thay-park-168-194864.html\">Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n: D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n th\u1ea7y Park</span><br>\r\n\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u chi\u1ec1u 19/8 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i. Th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-xau-ho-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-malaysia-168-194744.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/son-heungmin-xau-ho-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/son-heungmin-xau-ho-sau-tran-thua-soc-truoc-malaysia-168-194744.html\">Son Heung-min x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Tottenham, Son Heung-Min \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 17/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bao-chi-han-quoc-soc-nang-voi-that-bai-cua-doi-nha-tai-asiad-2018-472-194739.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/bao-chi-han-quoc-soc-nang-voi-that-bai-cua-doi-nha-tai-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/bao-chi-han-quoc-soc-nang-voi-that-bai-cua-doi-nha-tai-asiad-2018-472-194739.html\">B\u00e1o ch\u00ed H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ed1c n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 Kim chi c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh x\u1eed c\u1ee7a 1 v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong \u0111\u1ed9i sau khi thua tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5736","checkdouble":"194980"},{"date":"16:32 21/08","title":"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ecb d\u01a1 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain b\u1edfi \u1edf 4 l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng t\u1edbi 3. V\u00e0 h\u00e3y nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<h2>1. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U19 Bahrain (2016)</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U19 Bahrain t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u0103m 2016.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Bahrain nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Tr\u1ea7n Th\u00e0nh.\u00a0Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c1 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 VCK U20 World Cup 2017 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1edfi \u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 11 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, l\u00fac n\u00e0y Olympic Bahrain \u0111ang c\u00f3 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng thua U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eefa tr\u01b0\u1edbc Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn gi\u1eefa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn gi\u1eefa b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eebng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bahrain \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 U20 World Cup</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>2. Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-1 Olympic Bahrain (2010)</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ASIAD 2010, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u1ede b\u1ea3ng B c\u00f9ng Olympic Iran, Turkmenistan v\u00e0 Bahrain, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00fac \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ngay \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y \u00c1 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1 chung cu\u1ed9c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u0110inh Thanh Trung l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ph\u00fat 34 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e0 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c ghi th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Viet Nam 2010\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2010\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/viet-nam-bahrain-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u0103m 2010 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 Bahrain t\u1ea1i ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Bahrain sau nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 do Isa ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-3 \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n ASIAD n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-1 Olympic Bahrain c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD b\u1edfi nh\u1edd 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang ta ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<h2>3. \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam 5-3 Bahrain (2007)</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m VCK Asian Cup 2007, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Bahrain \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 th\u01b0\u1edfng, v\u00f4 ph\u1ea1t, hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 c\u1edfi m\u1edf v\u00e0 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn t\u1edbi 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho NHM.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Abdulrahman l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 3 sau sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n D\u01b0\u01a1ng H\u1ed3ng S\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau \u0111\u00f3, V\u0103n Nhi\u00ean, C\u00f4ng Vinh v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfn Th\u00e0nh l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf c\u00e1c ph\u00fat 11, 16 v\u00e0 52 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i 3-1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, s\u1ef1 l\u01a1 l\u00e0 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00fap Bahrain c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n g\u1ee1, tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00eam hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Thanh B\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c 5-3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Malaysia c\u1ee7a BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam-168-194974.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chinh-thuc-da-co-ban-quyen-asiad-tai-viet-nam-168-194974.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 tr\u00ean to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 l\u00e3nh th\u1ed5 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5735","checkdouble":"194992"},{"date":"17:09 21/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u1eeba qua, trong khi L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 suy ngh\u0129 kh\u00e1c.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qatar v\u00e0 Bangladesh, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Worrawoot Srimaka ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng B v\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 24 n\u0103m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out ASIAD. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Bao-chi-Thai-Lan-chi-trich-doi-nha-sau-that-bai-o-Asiad-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tr\u00e1i chi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd Siamsport gi\u1eadt d\u00f2ng t\u00edt th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn: \u201c\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nam Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t\u201d. T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch hai y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 do L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT) v\u00e0 HLV Worrawoot Srimaka.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Siamsport cho r\u1eb1ng FAT \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, HLV Srimaka l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Siamsport, t\u1edd Bangkok Post cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan \u1edf ASIAD 2018 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec7n ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i U23 trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan Somyot Poompunmuang \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u00eanh v\u1ef1c HLV Worrawoot Srimaka. \u201cL\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u1ea5y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3m t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1ed7i khi m\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1eb3ng HLV n\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng sa th\u1ea3i HLV Worrawoot. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean logic. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng C\u0110V Th\u00e1i Lan c\u0169ng n\u00ean c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn logic\u201d.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Malaysia c\u1ee7a BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5734","checkdouble":"195000"},{"date":"17:44 21/08","title":"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Bahrain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/19/bao-han-quoc-len-tieng-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-bahrain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd Chosun (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Bahrain, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng E t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Chosun (H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c) \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Bahrain-Khi-ASIAD-bay-gio-moi-thuc-s-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00e1o Chosun H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, s\u1ef1 tr\u1ed7i d\u1eady c\u1ee7a Bahrain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Bahrain c\u00e0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e0ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd thua H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1edbi 0-6 nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Kyrgyzstan v\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Malaysia 3-2. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c cao \u0111\u1ed9 n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain\", t\u1edd Chosun vi\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Song tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Bahrain c\u00f2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Iran. Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eabn c\u00f2n d\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Chosun, t\u1edd b\u00e1o Hankooki c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c l\u1ea1i tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\u0110\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Bahrain, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. N\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u Palestine \u2013 Syria\".\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/26/Khep-lai-VCK-U19-chau-A-2016-Buoc-ngoat-lich-su-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhin-lai-nhung-tran-thua-cua-bong-da-bahrain-truoc-viet-nam-168-194992.html\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Bahrain tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Bahrain. V\u00e0 t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111ang nghi\u00eang h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-thai-phan-ung-the-nao-sau-man-trinh-dien-te-hai-cua-doi-nha-o-asiad-168-195000.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf ASIAD?</span><br>\r\nGi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Ch\u00f9a v\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ea1i ASIAD v\u1eeba qua, trong khi L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 suy...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-hoi-han-vi-de-thua-malaysia-168-194980.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1eabn \u00e2n h\u1eadn v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 thua Malaysia</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c xem th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Malaysia c\u1ee7a BHL \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1ecd v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh \u1edf ASIAD.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5733","checkdouble":"195003"},{"date":"15:47 21/08","title":"Cho\u00e1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Busquets \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/choang-voi-so-tien-pha-vo-hop-dong-cua-busquets-o-ban-hop-dong-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sergio Busquets, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 500 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sergio Busquets \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergio Busquets \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, anh c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sergio Busquets h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sergio Busquets h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/choang-voi-so-tien-pha-vo-hop-dong-cua-busquets-o-ban-hop-dong-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Sergio Busquets \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man City quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBusquets \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 311 tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp \u1edf La Liga. Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 7 b\u00e0n. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Barca c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Man City mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Busquets, HLV Pep Guardiola mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Etihad.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMan City ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 250.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/barca-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-man-city-vu-busquets-172-186636.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man xanh nh\u1eafm Sergio Busquets nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Fernandinho</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Busquets</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sergio Busquets, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 500 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Busquets cua Barca\" title=\"tien ve Busquets cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/2/Barca-len-tieng-vu-Man-City-mua-Sergio-Busquets-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Busquets</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Busquets v\u1edbi Barca c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2021, Barca d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 150.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sergio Busquets ngay trong th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 s\u1ebd g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Barca \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 35 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u00e0o gi\u1eefa th\u00e1ng 6 Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0ng Busquets t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018 ngo\u00e0i ra anh kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i khi m\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Busquets gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5732","checkdouble":"194983"},{"date":"15:55 21/08","title":"Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng nh\u1ea3 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d Rafinha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/barca-san-sang-nha-nguoi-thua-rafinha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Rafinha ra \u0111i. \u0110\u00edch \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Real Betis, \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rafinha kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRafinha tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona. Anh gia nh\u1eadp CLB t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2006 khi m\u1edbi 7 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh trai Thiago Alcantara. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, cho t\u1edbi nay, ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o Rafinha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Rafinha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho Inter Milan m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh. Rafinha tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca v\u1edbi t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Rafinha ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Rafinha ra \u0111i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/barca-san-sang-nha-nguoi-thua-rafinha.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Rafinha ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hay ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n Barca m\u1edbi t\u1eadu v\u1ec1 Arthur v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal trong khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Ivan Rakitic, Sergio Busquets. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, \u1edf c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecd m\u1edbi mua Malcom v\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Lionel Messi, Ousmane Dembele.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Betis</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCha v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Rafinha, Mazinho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi Seville \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Real Betis. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi h\u1ebft m\u00f9a 2018/19 k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNghe \u0111\u00e2u Barca s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Rafinha ra \u0111i. D\u00f9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a HLV Ernesto Valverde v\u1ec1 Rafinha. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca kh\u00f4ng xem c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Betis l\u1ea1i \u0111ang c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. H\u1ecd t\u1eebng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua l\u1ea1i Dani Ceballos t\u1eeb Real Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i v\u00e0 CLB c\u0169 c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i quan \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Barca tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-218-barca-dinh-ngay-don-pogba-184-194949.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8: Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-valencia-11-atletico-madrid-vong-1-la-liga-201819-328-194947.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Valencia 1-1 Atletico Madrid (V\u00f2ng 1 La Liga 2018/19)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lionel-messi-giup-barca-chien-thang-nguoi-argentina-lieu-co-chanh-long-180-194790.html\">Lionel Messi gi\u00fap Barca chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ch\u1ea1nh l\u00f2ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-ernesto-valverde-nhan-xet-bat-ngo-ve-lionel-messi-180-194785.html\">HLV Ernesto Valverde nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/lich-thi-dau/lionel-messi-lap-cot-moc-6000-tai-la-liga-181-194781.html\">Lionel Messi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 6000 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed La Liga</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5731","checkdouble":"194985"},{"date":"16:27 21/08","title":"Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Rakitic cho PSG?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/barca-chot-gia-ban-rakitic-cho-psg.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic cho PSG n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed ch\u1ecbu chi ra 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ivan Rakitic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic cho PSG n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 125 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic cho PSG n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 125 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/17/Barca-ban-Ivan-Rakitic-cho-PSG-neu-nhan-duoc-125-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rakitic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang nh\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca. Trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, anh duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ivan Rakitic trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh\u00a0tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Paris s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Barca b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic, PSG \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i PSG th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/2-doi-bong-o-ligue-1-dai-chien-vi-rakitic-180-194119.html\" target=\"_blank\">Monaco c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua Ivan Rakitic</span>, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 Ligue 1 v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic cho PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca b\u00e1n Ivan Rakitic cho PSG n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed ch\u1ecbu chi ra 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rakitic mo ty so truoc Betis\" title=\"Rakitic mo ty so truoc Betis\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/22/MU-mua-Rakitic-voi-gia-khong-tuong-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Rakitic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 125 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 125 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u00fang b\u1eb1ng kho\u1ea3n ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rakitic v\u1edbi Barca, \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u00e0 tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi PSG.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 chi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec1n mua Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe, n\u1ebfu chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua Rakitic nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt C\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh do UEFA quy \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Barca \u0111\u00f2i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn cho Ivan Rakitic cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u1edf l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5730","checkdouble":"194989"},{"date":"17:18 21/08","title":"Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua sao tr\u1ebb Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/8/barca-chot-gia-mua-adrien-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua Adrien Rabiot. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 h\u01a1n 50 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rabiot</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Andres Iniesta, Barcelona mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. H\u1ecd nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain, m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rabiot v\u1edbi PSG ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nBan \u0111\u1ea7u, Barca hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft. Nh\u01b0ng CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n PSG \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eadp t\u1eaft \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Rabiot \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua Adrien Rabiot 50 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua Adrien Rabiot 50 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Barca-chot-gia-mua-Adrien-Rabiot-50-trieu-Euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua Adrien Rabiot l\u00e0 50 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Blaugrana ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c, Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 mua Adrien Rabiot l\u00e0 50 tri\u1ec7u Euro kh\u00f4ng h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 Blaugrana cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n cho 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i sau ng\u00e0y 31 th\u00e1ng 8, Barca s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Rabiot. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 sung Arthur v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, HLV Ernesto Valverde v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 th\u00eam chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng Andre Gomes hay Denis Suarez \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7n thanh l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Barca. Gomes \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y qua Everton d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong khi Suarez s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Camp Nou.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Rabiot \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc mang v\u1ec1 ho\u1eb7c Filipe Luis (Atletico Madrid) ho\u1eb7c Juan Bernat (Bayern Munich) cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3 Lucas Digne cho Everton v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng cho Jordi Alba.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chot-gia-ban-rakitic-cho-psg-180-194989.html\">Barca ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Rakitic cho PSG?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-194914.html\">Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/barca-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen-voi-phat-bieu-ve-pogba-172-194533.html\">Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/roma-chuan-bi-bao-thu-barca-thanh-cong-180-194430.html\">Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u201cb\u00e1o th\u00f9\u201d Barca th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/alan-shearer-toi-se-khong-ngac-nhien-neu-pogba-toi-barca-172-194416.html\">Alan Shearer: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu Pogba t\u1edbi Barca\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5729","checkdouble":"194994"},{"date":"17:48 21/08","title":"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/08","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-2108.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 21/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec Bale, Real t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2108 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 2108 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Chuyen-nhuong-Real-Madrid-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-2108-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale khi\u1ebfn Real t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGareth Bale \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Lopetegui t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u1ecf ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Eden Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-180-194897.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-180-194897.html\">Real Madrid s\u1eafp chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</span><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 200 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong 2 tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien dao Edinson Cavani\" title=\"tien dao Edinson Cavani\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/Real-Madrid-sap-chi-200-trieu-euro-nang-cap-doi-hinh-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 mua Edinson Cavani</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani, theo Diario Gol \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chia tay Chelsea trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ea1n th\u00e2n ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Neymar s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yuri Berchiche, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Neymar \u1edf Paris Saint-Germain, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai kh\u00f4ng xa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Luka Modric ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Emilio Butragueno c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm Falcao n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Real Madrid \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 30 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Falcao c\u1ee7a Monaco, Los Blancos \u0111ang c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Karim Benzema \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Werner g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Leipzig</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Leipzig, Timo Werner s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Leipzig.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Robert Lewandowski</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Bayern Munich tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Robert Lewandowski \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Real v\u00e0 PSG \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valencia ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Rodrigo v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 107 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00eda Valencia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Rodrigo cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 107 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5728","checkdouble":"195004"},{"date":"16:44 21/08","title":"Morata \u0111\u1eb7t ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/morata-dat-ra-muc-tieu-lon-tai-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMorata \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00f9ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb BL\u0110 v\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Alvaro Morata c\u0169ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 Arsenal.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 ni\u1ec1m tin. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd tr\u00f4i qua ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u00f4i t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. T\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ghi tr\u00ean 30 b\u00e0n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ecdn, t\u00f4i th\u00edch ghi 15-20 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League h\u01a1n, ho\u1eb7c danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\" title=\"Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong v\u00f2ng 1 th\u00e1ng v\u1eeba qua. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111ang \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u1ebfu Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c theo h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 CLB n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal. T\u1ea1i Premier League, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e0y&rdquo; &ndash; Alvaro Morata mu\u1ed1n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu-172-194971.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/eden-hazard-se-ngay-lap-tuc-roi-chelsea-neu-172-194971.html\">Eden Hazard s\u1ebd ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c r\u1eddi Chelsea n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nEden Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2019 n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd The Sun \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea-172-194932.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-chi-ra-ly-do-khien-arsenal-that-bai-truoc-chelsea-172-194932.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 ra l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Arsenal th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea</span><br>\r\nIan Wright ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Alexandre Lacazette l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5727","checkdouble":"194991"},{"date":"17:45 21/08","title":"B\u1ea1n c\u0169 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/jason-denayer-sap-roi-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng \u0103n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lyon h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5p thu\u1eadn t\u1eeb CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Denayer kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Man City</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJason Denayer t\u1eebng c\u00f3 5 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o \u1edf l\u00f2 JMG n\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng t\u1edbi trung t\u00e2m Trung t\u00e2m th\u1ec3 thao H\u00e0m R\u1ed3ng (Gia Lai) \u0103n t\u1eadp c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb HAGL bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd tay b\u1eaft m\u1eb7t m\u1eebng, \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u sau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu gi\u1eefa Man City v\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2015.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m 2013, Denayer chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb Man City. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb CLB v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Celtic, Galatasaray hay Sunderland. Tuy nhi\u00ean, anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh to\u00e0n sao c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ebfn Lyon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/jason-denayer-sap-roi-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Lyon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDenayer kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Man City v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn \u01b0a th\u00edch l\u00e0 Lyon c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ban \u0111\u1ea7u The Citizens kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t anh. H\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y sang ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u201canh em\u201d c\u00f9ng t\u1eadp \u0111o\u00e0n City Football Group l\u00e0 Girona d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Jason Denayer s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Man City \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Lyon. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 10 tri\u1ec7u Euro (9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) v\u00e0 r\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh t\u1eeb Man City. Th\u00f4ng qua Twitter, Man City c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y: \u201cCh\u00fac may m\u1eafn, Jason Denayer, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Lyon.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng bao g\u1ed3m ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, Denayer s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Lyon. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u201cS\u01b0 t\u1eed s\u00f4ng Rhone\u201d c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch Ligue 1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 ch\u1ec9 sau Paris Saint-Germain v\u00e0 Monaco.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-len-ke-hoach-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-john-stones-172-194898.html\">Man City l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-city-chi-60-trieu-bang-mua-ruben-neves-vao-thang-1-172-194884.html\">Man City chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ruben Neves v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/patrick-roberts-sap-roi-man-city-sang-girona-172-194473.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t sao tr\u1ebb chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sterling-toa-sang-tro-lai-guardiola-cau-khan-gia-han-voi-man-city-172-194465.html\">Sterling t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Guardiola c\u1ea7u kh\u1ea9n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-co-vai-dieu-muon-gui-den-man-city-va-sterling-172-194403.html\">Pep c\u00f3 v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Man City v\u00e0 Sterling</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pep-guardiola-man-city-het-tien-mua-cau-thu-roi-172-194212.html\">Pep Guardiola: \u201cMan City h\u1ebft ti\u1ec1n mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i!\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5726","checkdouble":"194995"},{"date":"17:13 21/08","title":"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd BBC c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a M.U. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/MU-sa-thai-Jose-Mourinho-bo-nhiem-Zinedine-Zidane--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n nh\u1eafm Zidane thay Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u00e0o Top 4 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, M.U nh\u1eafm Zinedine Zidane trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 Zidane n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU sa th\u1ea3i Jose Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zinedine Zidane l\u00e0 tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd BBC c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"MU ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/mu-phan-ung-ra-sao-sau-tin-don-sa-thai-mourinho-bo-nhiem-zidane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Zidane</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb M.U n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd BBC: \u201cT\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang ta l\u1ea1i n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn Zidane khi Mourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zidane thay Mourinho. BL\u0110 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Mourinho\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 M.U \u0111ang xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-va-bld-mu-mau-thuan-vi-anthony-martial-172-194990.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mourinho v\u00e0 BL\u0110 M.U c\u0169ng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1ec1 Martial</span>. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial ngay \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf l\u1ea1i Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5725","checkdouble":"194996"}]}